result.title: AtCoder Regular Contest 074 / Beginner Contest 062
result.content:
Two contests AtCoder Regular Contest 074 and AtCoder Beginner Contest 062 will be held at the same time.

You can participate in whichever contest you want. (However, you can't register to both competitions.) The last two tasks in ABC are the same as the first two tasks in ARC.

Time： May 20th (Saturday), 21:00 JST

Duration: 100 minutes

Number of Tasks: 4

writer： sugim48

Rating： 0-2799 for ARC, 0-1199 for ABC

The point value are:

ABC: 100 — 200 — 400 — 500 (300)

ARC: 400 — 500 (300) — 800 — 800

We are looking forward to your participation!

UPD: 7 hours to begin!
